data.description: Freshly remodeled 3bed, 2 bath home on 4 fenced and crossed fenced acres. Home has new metal roof, vinyl plank flooring throughout, new cabinets in kitchen and baths, tile showers, beautiful decks on front and back and Hardy board siding. If you have been searching for that quiet country life this one is for you.
